{"tid":273024,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"男朋友唔俾我著背心、裙","createTime":"2017-06-06T08:58:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-06T12:02:11.000Z","uid":10277,"like":3,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ff8db6930f3b182cf841e9835259a0997ccd741e","tid":273024,"uid":10277,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T08:58:58.000Z","msg":"利申左先我同男朋友係姐弟戀，差一年，但佢處事等等各方面都比較成熟，所以唔會出現我要照顧返佢轉頭，或者好似春嬌咁怕佢長唔大。<br />\n<br />\n入正題，其實成件事好簡單，就如題目所講佢唔俾我著背心、裙。Off shoulder就要成日都同佢一齊先著得。佢嘅原則係露肩ok，但露腰、露背、露胸就唔得。裙係因為佢怕我露底所以唔著得。短褲都可以接受。<br />\n<br />\n我知佢係擔心我先咁講，係男仔都唔想自己女朋友俾人睇洩，我明。咁但係大佬，女人都想靚啫。我唔係啲咩大波妹，係果啲飛機可以安全降落起飛形，我就唔信佢唔會係街望靚女<br />\n<br />\n女人有人望某程度都係榮幸黎<br />\n有時唔一定要大波，長腿，或者對波細細地先多人望<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d14a2c74cd473213891964229080f8ca142b41a","tid":273024,"uid":21423,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T09:00:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5b996939a4b58ebe9d6450472e98f5e7e7ee300d","tid":273024,"uid":4301,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T09:01:22.000Z","msg":"臭雞 ！"},{"pid":"1553aa3121ea0a23b20b7e27cbb279aa3eb6aba6","tid":273024,"uid":68081,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T09:04:12.000Z","msg":"佢真正意思我明。佢覺得你肥著得唔好睇，所以叫你咪著，你當局者迷唔明唔奇。你一定話唔係呀。。。。但對不起呢個問題只有男人先會心領身會，女人(no way)。。。。。。完。"},{"pid":"efeab009d2007f263528b5be9993b5dbc452e664","tid":273024,"uid":68081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T09:05:02.000Z","msg":"心領神會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee41e7e397486fa61feb7e0ad53ed003ba2cf54e","tid":273024,"uid":10277,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T09:06:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我著得不知幾靚"},{"pid":"1bdd72b04a78c3b08fb313d28f4a798908f74d01","tid":273024,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T09:06:48.000Z","msg":"咁鍾意俾人望去做雞囉"},{"pid":"f4bdf7bfb259a1d89d3911e06e295b568c3fe48e","tid":273024,"uid":68081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T09:08:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我著得不知幾靚</blockquote><br />\n那來的自信呀，臭g<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1198fa2543ceb29c2ec15e08afd38e0e8f93e9d9","tid":273024,"uid":62167,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T09:08:56.000Z","msg":"男人唔著裙都好正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f841a786a84ca0fee423c12c6e4c53660c676d88","tid":273024,"uid":52194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T09:08:56.000Z","msg":"一年姐咩弟戀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"043e0ba9d03b2bd93717238563545d34da6306d9","tid":273024,"uid":52237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T09:09:00.000Z","msg":"佢都係因為緊張你，驚你比人眼望望先咁講姐，如果你真係好渴望比其他人望，就你自己決定啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c264040c286d63b7499529a617f4f72ed07b31b3","tid":273024,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T09:10:02.000Z","msg":"同佢講，著裙方便野戰<br />\n<br />\n塊閪又唔會咁大味會好食啲"},{"pid":"6ac5998deec944c715e53f114ce728fb8ec0f086","tid":273024,"uid":62691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T09:11:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我著得不知幾靚</blockquote><br />\n圖"},{"pid":"3abd5596fa4468c598f24bedac8f834c139210a5","tid":273024,"uid":21837,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T09:12:13.000Z","msg":"有男朋友仲想周街俾人望<br />\n我唔明呢啲女人咩心態"},{"pid":"6d94cadfde9fcdcf1c7e0184dca7ba10782e